  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to study the effect of different levels of PEEP in ALI/ARDS patients on
      gas exchange.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In a population of ALI/ARDS patients during mechanical ventilation we will evaluate the
      effect of different levels of PEEP on gas exchange and dead space.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
